This project exists as a packaged app for Chrome.

  • https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ekbcoldneockcgfnaekhbpkigajjfneb

The application includes feature options such as toggling display of digits, horizontal / vertical layout, and daytime / nighttime mode.

Please see:

  Explanation of the algorithm:

    • https://github.com/tgiunipero/binary-clock/wiki/Explanation-of-the-algorithm

  Application namespace structure:

    • https://github.com/tgiunipero/binary-clock/wiki/Application-namespace-structure